#. Rockets_TinyYetBig.STRINGS.BUILDINGS.PREFABS.RTB_ADVANCEDLAUNCHPAD.DESC
msgctxt "Rockets_TinyYetBig.STRINGS.BUILDINGS.PREFABS.RTB_ADVANCEDLAUNCHPAD.DESC"
